  <ThingDef ParentName="AnimalThingBase">
    <defName>DE_Burrower</defName>
    <label>burrower</label>
    <description>Burrowers are weak larvae creatures that only have a life expectency of about a day. They seek out corpses that have begun to decompose, and burrow into them. Once inside, they will begin to metamorphize into a fungal servant depending on the body's size.</description>
