    <label>Metal Terror</label>
    <description>A mass of amalgamated fungal matter as well as several infected bodies, and most importantly, the consciousness of a live human. The Mikis Metalon Efialtis, or "Metal Terror", as many call it, is a lumbering behemoth of fungal might. It carries and breeds thousands of potent parasites in its body, which will latch onto anything it touches. The parasites consume the body from the inside and produce large amounts of spores, a process that almost looks like accelerated decomposition.</description>
